<li>6/28/95 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/ib210.html">The
 Dole-Johnson Bill: A Setback for Regulatory Reform?</a> by <a href="/townhall/herita
ge/staff/antonel.htm">Angela Antonelli</a>. (Issue Bulletin #210)
