<li>10/3/94 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/enviro/ib204.html">Superfund Status Quo: Why the Reauthorization Bills Won't Fix Superfund's Fatal Flaws</a> by John Shanahan. (Issue Bulletin #204)
<li>8/3/94 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/enviro/bg995.html">Clinton's "Voluntary" Global Warming Plan: Expensive, Ineffective, and Unnecessary</a> by John Shanahan. (Backgrounder 995, Published at 11 pages)
