<li>1/31/96 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/lect559.html">Making Regulatory Reform A Reality</a> by <a href="/heritage/staff/antonel.htm">Angela Antonelli</a>, Hon. David McIntosh, Fred Smith, and Dr. John Graham. (Lecture #559) 
