<a name="tax">
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<B><CENTER>TAXPAYER PROTECTION PLEDGE</CENTER></B>
<P>
<BR>
<BR>
<DD>I, ________, pledge to the taxpayers of the _____ District of the State of _______, <BR>and to the American people that I will
<P>
<DD>ONE, Oppose any and all efforts to increase the marginal income tax rates for individuals and/or businesses; and
<P>
<DD>    TWO, Oppose any further reduction or elimination of deductions and credits, unless matched dollar for dollar by further reducing tax rates.
<P>
<BR>
<BR>
Signed
<P>
<H4><B>Presidential Candidates who have signed the Pledge</B></H4>
Robert Dole<BR>
Harry Browne<BR>
<P>
<H4><B>Candidates who have refused</B></H4>
Bill Clinton
<p><br><p>
