Keleher, Robert E., William N. Cox, and William P. Orzechowski. 1982.  "The Flat-Rate Income Tax: Boon or Boondoggle?" <I>Economic Review</I>, Federal Reserve Bank of Atlanta
     (September), pp. 24-30.
<blockquote>
