428 U.S. 52 (1976).

<p>

<li>American Library Association, Intellectual Freedom Manual, 
Fourth Edition, 43 (1992).  The American Civil 
Liberties Union has long sought to protect the &quot;right&quot;
of children's access to pornography. NAMBLA, the North
American Man Boy Love Association, is another advocate for children's
&quot;sexual freedom.&quot;

<p>

<li><I>Id.</I>

